  "stats": {
    "bio": "Cell biologist and expert in human behavior — author, speaker, and founder of Al-Warsheh. Dr. Ghattass works to restore balance to individuals, institutions, and communities through a message that speaks to the human at their core. He weaves behavioral science, philosophy, cultural understanding, and art into a singular voice — translating complex academic concepts into deeply human stories. With more than two million followers across digital platforms, he has delivered hundreds of lectures and workshops across the Arab world.",
    "media": "Trained at Harvard, Cornell, Stanford, and the American University of Beirut. Published across major regional and international platforms.",
    "cta": "Learn more"
  },
